            "editor": "<p>Whether you're launching your first business, looking for a clearer path to growth, or simply exploring what's possible, Moonrock is here to help you move forward with confidence. Choose the path that feels right for you.</p>",
            "align": "center", "text_color": "rgba(255,255,255,0.75)", "width": { "unit": "px", "size": 720 }
          }
        },
        {
